Run this checklist before finalizing every website. Every "No" is a problem to fix.

| Check | Pass? |
|-------|-------|
| The first screen communicates the offer within 3 seconds | ☐ |
| The H1 is clear, specific, and keyword-relevant | ☐ |
| The page has one clear primary CTA visible without scrolling | ☐ |
