| Section spacing is premium (not cramped or empty) | ☐ |
| Typography has clear hierarchy: Display → H1 → H2 → H3 → Body | ☐ |
| Font pairing is deliberate and appropriate for the brand | ☐ |
| Color system is defined and based on brand psychology | ☐ |
| All text meets WCAG AA contrast requirements | ☐ |
| The mobile layout is excellent, not just "functional" | ☐ |
| Navigation is clear, accessible, and CTA-equipped | ☐ |
| Every section has a clear purpose that advances the user journey | ☐ |
| Social proof appears before the final CTA | ☐ |
| FAQ or objection handling is present | ☐ |
| The hero is not decoration — it explains and converts | ☐ |
| Animations are subtle, purposeful, and reduced-motion safe | ☐ |
