| One H1, logical H2/H3 structure, proper semantic HTML | ☐ |
| All interactive elements are keyboard navigable | ☐ |
| Focus states are visible and styled | ☐ |
| Forms have visible labels and accessible error states | ☐ |
| No horizontal overflow on any viewport width | ☐ |
